{"prompt": "Create an inviting website for a children's educational program. The layout should feature a cheerful sky blue.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Bright Minds Academy</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #87CEEB; /* Sky Blue */\n            color: #333;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #4682B4; /* Steel Blue - darker shade of sky blue */\n            color: #FFF;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); /* Slightly transparent white */\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 15px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #4682B4; /* Steel Blue */\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .program-highlights, .call-to-action {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .program-highlights ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n        .program-highlights li {\n            background-color: #ADD8E6; /* Light Blue */\n            padding: 15px 20px;\n            margin: 10px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            flex-basis: 250px; /* Minimum width for items */\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .program-highlights li:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n        .call-to-action p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #FFD700; /* Gold - cheerful accent */\n            color: #4682B4; /* Steel Blue */\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 25px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #DAA520; /* Darker Gold */\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #4682B4; /* Steel Blue */\n            color: #FFF;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: auto; /* Pushes footer to the bottom */\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            box-shadow: 0 -2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Bright Minds Academy</h1>\n        <p>Igniting Curiosity, Inspiring Futures</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Welcome to a World of Learning and Fun!</h2>\n        <p>At Bright Minds Academy, we believe in nurturing young minds through engaging activities, creative play, and a supportive environment. Our programs are designed to foster a lifelong love for learning in every child.</p>\n\n        <section class=\"program-highlights\">\n            <h2>Our Program Highlights</h2>\n            <ul>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Early Literacy</h3>\n                    <p>Fun phonics and reading games.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Creative Arts</h3>\n                    <p>Painting, drawing, and crafting adventures.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>STEM Exploration</h3>\n                    <p>Hands-on science and math activities.</p>\n                </li>\n                <li>\n                    <h3>Social Skills</h3>\n                    <p>Teamwork and collaboration through play.</p>\n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"call-to-action\">\n            <h2>Ready to Spark Your Child's Potential?</h2>\n            <p>Join our vibrant community and watch your child thrive!</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More & Enroll</a>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Bright Minds Academy. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Contact us: info@brightminds.com | 555-123-4567</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}